Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 你触犯了禁忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了发誓要封闭的心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能再把这份工作交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起回地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.10,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后接受罪孽的惩戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不能允许的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 我不会让你去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐好像没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.10,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要去哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐现在还被强烈的怨念所支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我也要出手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要从头开始吗 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.10,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}试缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么仙太郎没有救爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一明白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸的事就由我来告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把阿一还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把鸫交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见都不想见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想重归于好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛过的人还能相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不仅背叛我 还背叛了鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那个男的那儿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再出现在我们面前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个坏爸爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是自己的错却不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你爸爸能原谅她的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈就不会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能救她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有妈妈你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你把爸爸送下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐开始工作都过了那么多年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为惩罚 小姐她不得不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地狱受到的惩罚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐一直很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢长的岁月里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了时代一直注视着人们的怨恨所产生的结局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.70,0:08:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要怨恨这东西还在 想逃也逃不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花上无比漫长的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐一直在洗去罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自己的怨恨 封闭自己的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被你们父女 一下子解放出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖先是小姐怨恨的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的缘分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么告诉我这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是被命令了来看着我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我们也不知道该怎么办好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们是没有能力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只和小姐说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在叫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放你出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想让你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送他下去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把怨恨的对象送进地狱就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都在恨他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是假的 是你编造的虚假的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不知道那时候发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里还是一直在恨你爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我没那么想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为妈妈会死是爸爸的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说那么过分的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 把阿一还给我
