Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这次又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这是鸫最爱吃的点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 好痛 好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.20,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最爱的爸爸夺走了你的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难受吧 如果撕心裂肺一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会轻松的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线 敞开你的心扉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再痛苦了 让我成为鸫的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让鸫做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只要这个人原谅她的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就不用死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就会在鸫身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用那么寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 那和你没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的妈妈 都是那个人的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来制裁他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.90,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的是我就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是相信她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有原谅她 一时火起 不知如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 对不起 是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的死都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在道歉也晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的事情就无法挽回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔是没有意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西已经无法挽回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线 我帮你报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 最喜欢你的笑脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才努力工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那让你过得寂寞 渴望关怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却没原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还希望你死了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然真发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没能帮你承受那份痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我净给重要的人们添麻烦 伤害他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫很痛苦吧 寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 解开绳线吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你乱说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有觉得痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿一在一起可开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢阿一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一不开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起欢笑的时候都是假的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃饭 看电视 买东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然妈妈不在 偶尔也会寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有阿一 爸爸在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没事 不会痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.20,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和我在一起时痛苦吗 不开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.20,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和你在一起 我就感觉很幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱就是小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.20,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜欢仙太郎的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一直是最喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直都很后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后才造了那座庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的七童寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把寺给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.20,0:22:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.10,0:22:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我孤零零一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我保证
