Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.70,0:24:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要结果好就万事大吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.00,0:24:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口如果能愈合就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.70,0:24:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一旦醒悟过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.60,0:24:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的伤口还是一样疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.90,0:24:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 还是没有终结啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.20,0:24:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是可悲至极的生物啊
